metadata.name: Dobby
metadata.description:
Dobby doesn't even know why he's called Dobby.  Some quirk of the incoming overlords, based on their ancient culture.  Nor is he clear why they call his people aliens, when they are actually the natives of this planet.

But he can scrape a living on the streets of his old town as long as he keeps his distance from the other "superior" races and professions.  Just don't expect him to do it with a cheerful grin.
